# Bresser 6in1

## Readings:

## Coding

FSK with 100 us bit-width PCM.

    Oh, it's actually (120µs not 100µs):
rtl_433 -s 1M -X 'n=Bresser-6in1,m=FSK_PCM,s=120,l=120,r=2500'
